    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 at MRL 2. RH < 1 satisfied across all 5 COU operating points with margin. The primary validation dataset (ds01, dataVintage 2025-08-22) predates the modelRevisionDate (2025-09-15) by 24 days; the assessment team reviewed the revision change log and determined that the volute trailing-edge mesh refinement does not alter the hemolysis scalar field in the impeller passage where the RH QoI is computed. On this basis, formal re-validation against the revised model was not conducted. The credibility package is accepted at Medium assurance level for the CPB COU.",
